{
  "stem": "18486.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he sent them to his mother-- or-- or his mother-in-law, that I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, we knew that the package was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My husband went there because when-- when Jan was taken, we knew that they would go to his family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he went to his mother-in-law and said, give me the package.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know you have it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he brought it to us and we hid it in our garden.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't know that he had done that, because we didn't tell each other the things we did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was much better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- so, but when I saw him digging, then, so, that's how I found out that we had that stuff.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then when the Germans came and said, you have-- because [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Joel ?] had said that it was-- or somebody had told that it was with his mother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And his mother-in-law said, no, it's not with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when he pressed her, she said, well the last one I know who had it was Aart Vos, which was my husband.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so they came to our house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And how did it happen again-- oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We kept denying it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They brought-- they brought-- I-- no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had taken Jan Bartelsman, that was the one with whom we were in this thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And Jan Bartelsman came in shackles and his whole face all bruised, and terrible shape.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he said-- the-- the Germans who brought him to us, shackled-- said that Jan had confessed that we had this package-- under torture, of course.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we said-- we denied it, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We said-- and my husband wasn't home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was alone home with the children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, no, I don't-- absolutely don't know what package.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What is the package?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
